{"tid":1361481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔解決呢兩個問題，727一定會有傷亡","createTime":"2019-07-24T15:21:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T04:10:30.000Z","uid":260370,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"344c639c2659f4b5d35839df708ce93166ed8a96","tid":1361481,"uid":260370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:21:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">第一，前線共識要果斷執行。尤其是走既共識。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n上環嗰次前線九點宣言完左已經開咪叫人be water散水叫走架喇。<br />\n<br />\n去到十點上環路口防線因地勢太差，又一次有共識，先退回中環再作打算。<br />\n<br />\n但大家又係等埋前面先走，前面唔走我唔走，前面又話後面走咗我先走，最後大家等大家坐哂係度，無人走。<br />\n<br />\n結局就係前線有手足屌哂鬼傷和氣，之後大家又局住留係上環硬碰硬。搞到有手足受哂傷。<br />\n<br />\n呢樣野唔係第一次，沙田又係同樣問題，又係前線屌哂鬼都無人肯陏，最後就比人夾到入新城市混戰。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">呢個問題嚴重影響和氣同錯失時機！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n對住差佬你錯先走既時機你比會人暴力清場。對住鄉黑你錯失走既時機，喺入面留耐左一陣，分分鐘連之前入村條路都比人封埋。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第二，要諗定辦法對付惡犬（真正既狗）</span></span><br />\n<br />\n要知道鄉黑有好多狗。佢哋完全有能力一次過放上百隻狗咬人。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">我哋啲gear都係防人防煙為主，對付狗隻真係無經驗</span></span>，可能幾十隻狗已經令前線受傷。甚至佢哋本身都唔洗出嚟打人，從狗場一車車敢運狗，我哋已經收皮。<br />\n<br />\n請各位手足認真諗下計。"},{"pid":"890aae4a9cd5a1d1d78608aa4aa985df0af8ccaa","tid":1361481,"uid":260370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:21:51.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"f3f92b629e2da4d675a3108aa5083a017f0d449d","tid":1361481,"uid":260370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:24:17.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac18ff032a4acd72d1d119f004954f8c768656c9","tid":1361481,"uid":260370,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:27:13.000Z","msg":"pish<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd28342b57f5b63d69e13bda28af6c4564a36d9e","tid":1361481,"uid":191290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:30:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好撚重要！唔該幫手推啊！！推得好辛苦！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【唔想輸嘅入嚟幫手置頂】如何避免被人鳩帶風向+攻破白色恐怖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1361315\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1361315</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4fdcd30f93e3fe1dc31d772d7230d28cc87fd863","tid":1361481,"uid":126280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:32:49.000Z","msg":"第一條：後面要決斷，相信前線，我地走，佢哋先會走！<br />\n<br />\n第二條：聽講狗唔食得麥提莎（未fact check）"},{"pid":"06758f13679621f564d9c932677c5c600b142ed2","tid":1361481,"uid":280683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:33:09.000Z","msg":"後面吾知前面咩情況<br />\n最好前面決定走吾走<br />\n後面尊重前面既決定<br />\n前面向後，後面自然會向後<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">不割席，不分化</span>"},{"pid":"ebcdfb3976fe07066f21eb9fa612337101df706d","tid":1361481,"uid":170987,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:33:50.000Z","msg":"前線唔肯走可以點？"},{"pid":"01fe91b7c9a8d516e97e0d23e6653b10ad166310","tid":1361481,"uid":245409,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:34:29.000Z","msg":"最緊要唔好放火呀大佬"},{"pid":"64f7cf1612a96fe5f32a9bf0ecc17260eb6a5edd","tid":1361481,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:36:07.000Z","msg":"對狗要用狗糧定朱古力"},{"pid":"628d630d7d1d0772c71f3376706abfdd93924649","tid":1361481,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T15:36:20.000Z","msg":"狗好似怕高頻，同濃味"}